464
00:58:23,511 --> 00:58:30,110
So don’t you think you have to do it?

465
00:58:30,110 --> 00:58:33,400
So humble down yourself!

466
00:58:33,400 --> 00:58:36,691
Humble down yourself in your heart.

467
00:58:36,691 --> 00:58:39,521
Humble down in your heart.

468
00:58:39,521 --> 00:58:41,080
Enjoy your humility.

469
00:58:41,080 --> 00:58:43,801
Enjoy your virtues.

470
00:58:43,801 --> 00:58:48,041
The greatest virtue of a Sahaj Yogi is humility.

471
00:58:48,041 --> 00:58:54,890
Now, so many things you have seen to convince
you.

472
00:58:54,890 --> 00:59:03,711
But in no way it can mean any kind of subjection,
because what subjection you can give me?

473
00:59:03,711 --> 00:59:06,090
Think of that.

474
00:59:06,090 --> 00:59:15,001
When every subjection is a blessing, what
subjection you are giving?

475
00:59:15,001 --> 00:59:21,031
Every feeling in the heart is a blessing.

476
00:59:21,031 --> 00:59:30,180
Just now you feel it and you feel the joy,
in your heart.

477
00:59:30,180 --> 00:59:31,751
Then what is your subjection?

478
00:59:31,751 --> 00:59:33,971
About what?

479
00:59:33,971 --> 00:59:38,741
I can understand people who are just newly
come, who are good for nothing.

480
00:59:38,741 --> 00:59:41,301
But you are not on the periphery.

481
00:59:41,301 --> 00:59:45,071
But some of them do go into periphery in no
time.

482
00:59:45,071 --> 00:59:47,560
You give them some work — finished!

483
00:59:47,560 --> 00:59:49,600
If I am sweet to someone — finished!

484
00:59:49,600 --> 00:59:51,170
If I see someone — finished!

485
00:59:51,170 --> 00:59:52,660
I mean, this is too much.

486
00:59:52,660 --> 01:00:04,441
I can’t even be nice to you.

487
01:00:04,441 --> 01:00:10,851
If you do any mistakes or anything, then you
get your left Vishuddhi.

488
01:00:10,851 --> 01:00:14,491
You’ve done your mistake, all right, finish
it.

489
01:00:14,491 --> 01:00:15,751
You love me.

490
01:00:15,751 --> 01:00:20,221
Maybe there’s something wrong in the love
or maybe something has happened, doesn’t

491
01:00:20,221 --> 01:00:21,221
matter.

492
01:00:21,221 --> 01:00:23,560
“Now, I’m going to be cautious.

493
01:00:23,560 --> 01:00:25,900
I’m not going to make any mistakes.

494
01:00:25,900 --> 01:00:27,930
How could I do this mistake?

495
01:00:27,930 --> 01:00:30,560
Because I was not fully in love.

496
01:00:30,560 --> 01:00:33,861
If I had loved something, I would have not
done such a mistake!”

497
01:00:33,861 --> 01:00:36,411
All right, so develop your love.

498
01:00:36,411 --> 01:00:37,411
No.

499
01:00:37,411 --> 01:00:43,971
your will do, “I feel guilty because I have
done such a thing."

500
01:00:43,971 --> 01:00:45,781
So you miss this and that both.

501
01:00:45,781 --> 01:00:48,451
So your mistake becomes a barrier again.

502
01:00:48,451 --> 01:00:50,771
Don’t feel guilty about it.

503
01:00:50,771 --> 01:00:52,301
We have to progress further.

504
01:00:52,301 --> 01:00:53,491
Forget the past.

505
01:00:53,491 --> 01:00:54,491
Forget the past.

506
01:00:54,491 --> 01:00:55,491
Forget the past.

507
01:00:55,491 --> 01:00:56,491
We have to go further.

508
01:00:56,491 --> 01:00:58,361
We have to be serious people.

509
01:00:58,361 --> 01:01:06,331
When we talk, we should talk with that dignity
of that awe.

510
01:01:06,331 --> 01:01:17,670
That’s very important and once you develop
that awe your Ekadasha will disappear.

511
01:01:17,670 --> 01:01:20,731
Ekadasha will disappear.

512
01:01:20,731 --> 01:01:27,501
Just think of the awe.

513
01:01:27,501 --> 01:01:45,551
See the silence and the joy, and the joy of
the awe is deep, very deep, like a sea.

514
01:01:45,551 --> 01:01:53,430
The sea on superficial level is very turbulent,
but inside is silent, absolutely silent.

515
01:01:53,430 --> 01:01:55,491
Feel that depth.

516
01:01:55,491 --> 01:02:04,320
Without awe, you cannot go down.

517
01:02:04,320 --> 01:02:12,050
I have sometimes even said little loudly some
things to Warren, I know, but it’s never,

518
01:02:12,050 --> 01:02:13,840
never felt with him.

519
01:02:13,840 --> 01:02:21,211
But with some people I have never said because
I know the person won’t take it from me.

520
01:02:21,211 --> 01:02:34,920
But he never feels that I have said anything
wrong or to hurt him in any way, that’s

521
01:02:34,920 --> 01:02:45,080
the sign of complete awe.

522
01:02:45,080 --> 01:02:53,711
And it’s just a wee bit of penetration,
a very little bit of penetration [that’s

523
01:02:53,711 --> 01:02:54,961
needed].

524
01:02:54,961 --> 01:02:57,160
Forget the self-importance.

525
01:02:57,160 --> 01:02:59,871
Forget the greatness that you think about
yourself.

526
01:02:59,871 --> 01:03:07,410
When you become the zero then you become nirmala.

527
01:03:07,410 --> 01:03:15,050
As long as you are like a cup, you are small.

528
01:03:15,050 --> 01:03:23,021
When the boundaries of the cups are broken,
there’s no more a cup.

529
01:03:23,021 --> 01:03:26,791
And this is what today I have to tell you.

530
01:03:26,791 --> 01:03:39,231
Today is the eleventh day and ten days, out
of which nine days were the periods of fights.

531
01:03:39,231 --> 01:03:44,110
Tenth day is the period of victory.

532
01:03:44,110 --> 01:03:49,810
Now eleventh day is of enjoyment.

533
01:03:49,810 --> 01:03:53,870
But how can the people who do not have the
awe, enjoy?

534
01:03:53,870 --> 01:04:00,370
I cannot understand.

535
01:04:00,370 --> 01:04:07,261
Because Ekadasha forms the barrier.

536
01:04:07,261 --> 01:04:11,541
And the barrier of Ekadasha, you know what
it is.

537
01:04:11,541 --> 01:04:21,551
Feel the awe and you’ll go deep into your
heart, deep into your heart.

538
01:04:21,551 --> 01:04:28,981
Because you are at a point where just you
have to have the gravity to go down.

539
01:04:28,981 --> 01:04:37,711
[It’s] working out: try to keep that.

540
01:04:37,711 --> 01:04:45,481
Slowly and slowly you all have come up to
a point only thing is now develop your depth.

541
01:04:45,481 --> 01:04:47,590
Go deep down.

542
01:04:47,590 --> 01:04:52,711
I know there are frivolous people but they’ll
all be dropped out in no time.

543
01:04:52,711 --> 01:04:54,920
Don’t worry about them.

544
01:04:54,920 --> 01:04:57,800
I know what people are doing, how they are
behaving.

545
01:04:57,800 --> 01:05:08,081
I know every one of you very well, each one
of you.

546
01:05:08,081 --> 01:05:16,830
So, respect your body, respect yourself, keep
your hamsas all right at least.

547
01:05:16,830 --> 01:05:24,241
And I am sure, if you become serious about
it…you need a serious understanding of the

548
01:05:24,241 --> 01:05:26,831
whole thing, that’s what is lacking.

549
01:05:26,831 --> 01:05:33,880
Because if you love someone, the whole thing
becomes an entire possession sort of thing,

550
01:05:33,880 --> 01:05:43,951
the entire being is so seriously involved
into it that you cannot afford to miss anything.

551
01:05:43,951 --> 01:05:51,971
And that’s what is going to help you.

552
01:05:51,971 --> 01:05:59,670
But seriousness never means you are not enjoying.

553
01:05:59,670 --> 01:06:04,610
Enjoyment is so deep: it’s pouring into
the heart.

554
01:06:04,610 --> 01:06:07,370
I play with you.

555
01:06:07,370 --> 01:06:10,951
I always try to say things that will please
you.

556
01:06:10,951 --> 01:06:15,860
And it should please you much more that I
have said — what today is that — how to

557
01:06:15,860 --> 01:06:23,211
reach your depths, to reach that gravity that
will make you the gurus.

558
01:06:23,211 --> 01:06:32,461
Today I had to talk to you like a guru, because
I feel that now the time has come for all

559
01:06:32,461 --> 01:06:38,211
of you to become gurus of the right type.

560
01:06:38,211 --> 01:06:47,670
Not with egos or talking big and creating
a big sort of a show out of you.

561
01:06:47,670 --> 01:06:59,491
But a definite depth within you that people
see that, “Here is a beacon of Mother."

562
01:06:59,491 --> 01:07:03,761
And it is so fantastic!

563
01:07:03,761 --> 01:07:11,581
The whole thing is so great, to be that.

564
01:07:11,581 --> 01:07:18,660
This is what the gurus used to do, first of
all, is to cleanse people, clear them out,

565
01:07:18,660 --> 01:07:24,481
take out their barriers, make them take out
their egos, by hanging them round, putting

566
01:07:24,481 --> 01:07:29,100
them on top of a well, putting them down five,
six times, dipping them down.

567
01:07:29,100 --> 01:07:33,691
They used to do all this for what?

568
01:07:33,691 --> 01:07:51,691
But now you can do it because I am before
you!Because I have come.

569
01:07:51,691 --> 01:08:02,111
This is the reason.

570
01:08:02,111 --> 01:08:05,801
Understand what Warren has, so rightly, said.

571
01:08:05,801 --> 01:08:10,350
You might say that “Mother was working through
him."

572
01:08:10,350 --> 01:08:12,340
Maybe.

573
01:08:12,340 --> 01:08:17,031
But, I always work through you if you are
one with me.

574
01:08:17,031 --> 01:08:20,830
Even when I am speaking, you are speaking.

575
01:08:20,830 --> 01:08:23,791
And when you are speaking, I am speaking.

576
01:08:23,791 --> 01:08:27,930
You know that.

577
01:08:27,930 --> 01:08:39,920
But with all this, that awe is very important.

578
01:08:39,920 --> 01:08:56,130
And that gives you the love that thinks: complete
integration of your heart and your brain.

579
01:08:56,130 --> 01:09:02,281
The love that thinks is thoughtful, the love
that thinks.

580
01:09:02,281 --> 01:09:08,910
And then the third integration: the love that
acts.

581
01:09:08,910 --> 01:09:22,040
But first this integration must be brought
in: the love that thinks, which understands,

582
01:09:22,040 --> 01:09:26,900
which feels.

583
01:09:26,900 --> 01:09:34,971
And then the love that acts.

584
01:09:34,971 --> 01:09:59,491
But the basic is the love — it starts from
the heart — is the love.

585
01:09:59,491 --> 01:10:06,491
I think you’d better take my tape today
and listen to it.

586
01:10:06,491 --> 01:10:07,851
Meditate.

587
01:10:07,851 --> 01:10:11,531
Meditate on that.

588
01:10:11,531 --> 01:10:24,410
I want to see my children in England develop
the depth in language, in speech, in feelings,

589
01:10:24,410 --> 01:10:29,331
in expressions, in the personality.

590
01:10:29,331 --> 01:10:36,180
It’s only the awe that will make it.

591
01:10:36,180 --> 01:10:41,120
But awe which is not frightening, but awe
that’s joy-giving.

592
01:10:41,120 --> 01:10:44,310
This is the integration of it.

593
01:10:44,310 --> 01:10:54,021
Awe that is joy-giving is not frightening.

594
01:10:54,021 --> 01:10:57,331
Open your hearts!

595
01:10:57,331 --> 01:11:03,441
But it doesn’t mean you should be frivolous,
[but] with all the care.

596
01:11:03,441 --> 01:11:05,650
Have you seen a lotus opening?

597
01:11:05,650 --> 01:11:14,180
How beautifully it opens: slowly, every petal
so careful not to hit each other.

598
01:11:14,180 --> 01:11:16,781
Slowly it opens out.

599
01:11:16,781 --> 01:11:24,951
And then the fragrance starts pouring in,
in the most dignified manner.

600
01:11:24,951 --> 01:11:43,820
Such a flower only can be offered at the Lotus
feet of the Adi Shakti, isn’t it?

601
01:11:43,820 --> 01:11:53,860
May God bless you.

